Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ leading directly to \Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation\

Name: Percentage of manuscripts that proceed from \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ to \Manuscript Export Succeeded\

Name: Number of times \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ occurs before \SW-Checklist Completed\

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ followed by \SW-AE Assign Reviewers\ within the same case
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ in relation to the total number of activities in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Percentage of cases where \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ leads to a \SW-EIC Reject\ decision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Number of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ activities that precede \Plagiarism Originality Report Completed\
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' occurs

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ activities that are followed by any form of reviewer agreement, such as \SW-Reviewer Agreed\
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ in manuscripts that require major revision, indicated by \SW-EIC Major Revision\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision' occurs

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ in the paths leading to \Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation\
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of variants including \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ and their average performance

Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ followed by \Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' for cases where activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1' occurs

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ in cases that eventually lead to \RW-EIC Accept\
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'RW-EIC Accept'

Name: Number of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ activities that are part of the longest and shortest variants in the process
